ing":0},"body":"This is the shortest example I can come up with: https://psalm.dev/r/73674a90ca\r\n\r\n```\r\n<?php\r\n  \r\n/**\r\n * @template T as object\r\n * @template S as object\r\n * @param array<T> $a\r\n * @param class-string<S> $type\r\n * @return array<T&S>\r\n */\r\nfunction filter(array $a, string $type): array {\r\n    $result = [];\r\n    foreach ($a as $item) {\r\n        if (is_a($item, $type)) {\r\n            $result[] = $item;\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n    return $result;\r\n}\r\n\r\ninterface A {\r\n    public function a(): void;\r\n}\r\n\r\ninterface B {\r\n    public function b(): void;\r\n}\r\n\r\nclass C implements A, B {\r\n    public function a(): void {}\r\n    public function b(): void {}\r\n}\r\n\r\n/** @var array<A> */\r\n$x = [];\r\n$y = filter($x, B::class);\r\n\r\nforeach ($y as $item) {\r\n    $item->a();\r\n    $item->b();\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nGives me \r\n\r\n```\r\nINFO: MixedMethodCall - 38:12 - Cannot determine the type of the object on the left hand side of this expression\r\n\r\nINFO: MixedMethodCall - 39:12 - Cannot determine the type of the object on the left hand side of this expression\r\n```\r\n","closed_by":{"login":"muglug","id":2292638,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIyOTI2Mzg=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2292638?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug","html_url":"https://github.com/muglug","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglug/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/muglu